---
title: Smoky Chicken Fajitas with Blistered Corn Salsa & Fresh Guacamole
description: Fajitas are the ultimate crowd pleaser, especially with fixings as delicious as these. We're upping your salsa game with smoky blistered corn and fresh tomatoes - you'll never open another jar again. Fiesty cumin and chili-spiked chicken plus creamy guacamole will make this a fajita night to remember.
